(1, '2019-09-11 08:22:33', '2019-09-11 08:22:33', '珠海市新霖科技有限公司是一家专业从事LED智能调光技术产品的研发，生产，销售及售后服务的高新技术企业。公司主要生产，可控硅/Triac 调光电源，0-10V调光电源，DALI调光驱动及无线控制产品等。产品兼容路创、邦奇、飞利浦、欧司朗、奇胜、施耐德等系统。广泛运用于酒店工程、LED亮化工程、广告灯箱、城市景观照明工程、商业照明、室内外照明工程、酒吧、KTV等各个大领域。公司拥有先进的生产设备，完善的生产流程、专业的技术工程师及一流的销售团队，始终坚持以优质的产品和至上的服务为立足之本，以客户需求为发展源泉，秉承“信誉第一，质量至上”的经验理念，生产出一流的产品，满足客户各种需求。珠海市新霖科技有限公司产品齐全，价格合理，产品畅销国内外，出口多个国家和地区。', 'Zhuhai sailing Technology Co., Ltd. is a high-tech enterprises engaged in LED intelligent dimming technology products research and development, production, sales and after-sales . The company mainly produces Triac dimming power supply, 0-10V/1-10 dimming driver, DALI dimming driver and wireless control products. Products are compatible with Lutron, Dynalite, Philips, Osram, Clipsal, Schneider and other brand systems. Widely used in hotel engineering, LED lighting engineering, advertising lighting, landscape lighting engineering, commercial lighting, indoor and outdoor lighting engineering, bars, KTV etc.. The company has advanced production equipment, perfect production process, professional technical engineers and first-class sales team, always adhere to high-quality products and supreme service as the basis, customer demand as the source of development, adhering to the \"reputation first, quality first\" experience concept, to provide globally competitive products to meet the needs of customers. Zhuhai sailing Technology Co., Ltd. has a full range of products, reasonable prices, best-selling products sales all over the world.', '广东省珠海市（南屏科技园）屏东2路20号', '1st Building, No.20, Pingdong 2th Road, Nanping Technical Industrial Park, Zhuhai, Guangdong, China', '+86-0756-8305964', '+86-013680337300', '+86-756-8305964', 'info@ledsailing.com');

