(1, '2019-09-11 12:13:47', '2019-09-16 17:34:00', 'LTD-P-030-12', '30W 12V/24V 可控硅恒压电源', '30W 12V/24V  Triac dimmable drivers', 6, 1, 1, '/public/uploads/images/2019-09-11/LTD-P-030-12-1.jpg|/public/uploads/images/2019-09-11/LTD-P-030-12-2.jpg|/public/uploads/images/2019-09-11/LTD-P-030-12-3.jpg|', '/public/uploads/images/2019-09-11/LTD-P-030-12-list.jpg', '<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><li><p>◆调光方式：可控硅调光，满足前沿（Triac）调光、后沿(ELV)调光<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span></p></li><li><p>◆高质量，体积小、寿命长<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>◆兼容性强，调光无闪烁，无抖动，调光曲线平滑<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>◆具备短路、过载、过压及保护<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>◆100%满负载老化<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>◆使用环境温度：-30℃~+50℃<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>◆电磁兼容符合EN55015、EN61000、EN61547<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>◆安规标准符合EN61347-1<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span></p></li></ul><p><br/></p>', '<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><li><p>Dimming type：Triac dimmable，<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"></span></p></li><li><p>High quality, small volume and long life<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>Strong compatibility, no flicker, no jitter, smooth dimming curve<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>Open circuit and short circuit protection<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>Output Protections: OLP/OVP/OTP<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>100% Full Load Aging Test<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>Work Temperature: -30℃~+50℃<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>EMC approval according to: EN55015, EN61000 and EN61547<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p></li><li><p>Conform to general and safety requirements IEC/EN 61347-1</p></li></ul><p><br/></p>', '<p>此系列恒压可控硅led调光驱动支持前沿切相和后沿切相调光器，可兼容路创、邦奇、飞利浦、欧司朗、奇胜、施耐德等多种品牌系统，实现平滑调光的效果。适用于LED灯带、LED霓虹灯、灯箱、发光字、景观灯等，广泛运用于酒店工程、LED亮化工程、广告灯箱、城市景观照明工程、商业照明、室内外照明工程、酒吧、KTV等各大领域。</p>', '<p>This series of constant current triac led dimming driver supports leading edge and trailing edge dimming, compatible with Lutron, Dynalite, Philips, Osram, Clipsal, Schneider and other brand systems to achieve smooth dimming effect.It is suitable for ceiling lamp, panel light, spotlight, tube lamp, etc. It is widely used in Hotel engineering, commercial lighting, indoor lighting engineering and other fields.&nbsp;</p>', '<table class=\"table table-hover table-bordered\"><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td>型号</td><td>LTD-M-060-12</td><td>LTD-M-060-24</td></tr><tr><td>输入电压</td><td colspan=\"2\">AC200～240VAC/ 100～130VAC</td></tr><tr><td>输出电流</td><td>5A</td><td>2.5A</td></tr><tr><td>输出电压</td><td>12VDC</td><td>24VDC</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">输出功率</td><td colspan=\"2\">60W</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">频率</td><td colspan=\"2\">50/60Hz</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">调光电压范围</td><td colspan=\"2\">0-100%</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">调光方式</td><td colspan=\"2\">前沿（Triac）调光、后沿(ELV)调光</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">效率</td><td colspan=\"2\">85%</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">使用环境温度</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\">-30℃~+50℃</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">外壳</td><td colspan=\"2\">金属壳</td></tr><tr><td>尺寸</td><td colspan=\"2\">255*49*30mm （L*W*H）</td></tr><tr><td>重量</td><td colspan=\"2\">0.5Kg</td></tr><tr><td>包装尺寸</td><td colspan=\"2\">36*32*22cm/20pcs</td></tr></tbody></table>', '<table class=\"table table-hover table-bordered\"><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td>Model</td><td colspan=\"2\">LTD-P-12-300</td></tr><tr><td>Input voltage</td><td colspan=\"2\">AC200～240VAC/ 100～130VAC</td></tr><tr><td>Output current</td><td>150-300mA</td><td>100-150mA</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\">Output voltage</td><td>DC 3-42V</td><td>DC50-72V</td></tr><tr><td>Power</td><td colspan=\"2\">3-