(1, '2018-09-11 07:57:30', '2019-09-14 21:16:04', '北京国际皇冠艺苑大酒店', 'CROWNE PLAZA Beijing', '<p>北京国际艺苑皇冠假日酒店设施完善、时尚，会议商务设施可满足各类需求，并提供充满动感和时尚科技的空间。酒店同时设有风格迥异的多元餐厅、酒吧等可供选择。其中部分照明采用新霖生产的LED调光电源。</p>', '<p>Crowne Plaza Beijing International Art Park is well-equipped, fashionable, conference and business facilities can meet all kinds of needs, and provide a space full of dynamic and fashion technology.The hotel also has a wide variety of restaurants and bars to choose from. Some of the LED lighting in this hotel uses the LED dimming power supply produced by SAILING</p>', '/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20190911/1568216927580470.jpeg', '/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20190911/1568216927580470.jpeg'),
(2, '2018-09-12 08:17:18', '2019-09-14 21:04:13', '常州锦江国际大酒店', 'Changzhou Jinjiang international hotel', '<p>常州锦江国际大酒店是由上海锦江国际酒店管理有限公司管理的集客房、餐饮、会务、休闲于一体的高星级豪华商务酒店。现有两百余间精致典雅、设备完善的客房。其中部分照明采用新霖生产的LED调光电源。</p>', '<p>Changzhou Jinjiang International Hotel is a high-star luxury hotel,the Business Inn managed by Shanghai Jinjiang International Hotel Management Co., Ltd. There are more than 200 exquisite and well-equipped guest rooms. Some of the LED lighting in this hotel uses the LED dimming power supply produced by SAILING</p>', '/public/uploads/images/2019-09-12/case-img2.jpg', '/public/uploads/images/2019-09-12/case-img2.jpg'),
(3, '2018-09-14 21:08:53', '2019-09-14 21:08:53', '千岛湖海外海假日酒店', 'Holiday Inn Hangzhou Thousand-Island Lake', '<p>千岛湖海外海假日酒店位于淳安千岛湖中心城区和名闻遐迩的千岛湖畔——开发路，近曙光路；周围依山傍水、风光旖旎、景色迷人，是长江三角洲的静谧后花园。其中部分照明采用新霖生产的LED调光电源。</p>', '<p>Holiday Inn Hangzhou Thousand-Island Lake is located in the center of Chun&#39;an Qiandao Lake and the famous Qiandao Lake-Development Road, near Shuguang Road; surrounded by mountains and water, beautiful scenery, charming scenery, is the quiet back garden of the Yangtze River Delta. Some of the LED lighting in this hotel uses the LED dimming power supply produced by SAILING</p>', '/public/uploads/images/2019-09-14/case-img4.jpg', '/public/uploads/images/2019-09-14/case-img4.jpg');

